by javiereguiluz at 2015-04-15T11:25:23Z

I've found a big problem in this proposal :cry:  It works perfectly for long names ... but it breaks the design for short names. The first alternative solution I can think of is using an image as the site name. The other one is using the following markup:

```yaml
easy_admin:
    site_name: '<div style="line-height: 1.3">My Company <br/> Our Project</div>'
```

What do you think of these solutions? Do you know any alternative CSS solution that we could use to keep both long and short names vertically centered? Thanks.

