by Pierstoval at 2015-05-13T18:22:03Z

Everything seems to work well in your screenshots.

There is no default support for "long" names in desktop, because we would need a letter-wrapping.
On mobile/tablet, the long name is simply modifying the width of its container, naturally.
I think we cannot have a "generic" function for this, because the design on mobile/tablet is restricted in height, and the design in desktop is restricted in width...

Maybe @ogizanagi you can find a better idea ? :)

